## Synq env example (do not commit real secrets)

# Jupiter Prediction API key (server-side only)
JUP_PREDICTION_API_KEY="replace-with-your-key"

# Optional: Jupiter API key for price + tokens enrichment and sync script
# - Enriches /api/jup/stocks with liquidity, holders, 24h stats
# - Run `npm run sync-rwa-stocks` to fetch all stock mints into lib/rwa-tokens-generated.json
# JUPITER_API_KEY="your-jupiter-api-key"

# Optional: Solana RPC used by the client for signing + sending
NEXT_PUBLIC_SOLANA_RPC_URL="https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com"

# Admin wallet allowlist (comma separated)
ADMIN_WALLET_ADDRESSES=""

